Package: climbr
Title: Data Preparation and Analysis for Climbing Ratings
Version: 3.0.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Dean",
           family = "Scarff",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dos@scarff.id.au",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6681-7190"))
Description: Support functions for fitting climbing ascent data to a Whole-History Rating model.  These functions wrangle data in formats exposed by theCrag.com, preparing it for analysis with the Python climbing_ratings package.  They also provide analysis of the fitted model (plotting charts etc.).
